proguard.classfile.kotlin.flags

Class KotlinFlags

  • java.lang.Object
    • proguard.classfile.kotlin.flags.KotlinFlags
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KotlinClassFlags, KotlinCommonFlags, KotlinConstructorFlags, KotlinEffectExpressionFlags, KotlinFunctionFlags, KotlinModalityFlags, KotlinPropertyAccessorFlags, KotlinPropertyFlags, KotlinTypeAliasFlags, KotlinTypeFlags, KotlinTypeParameterFlags, KotlinValueParameterFlags, KotlinVisibilityFlags

    public abstract class KotlinFlags
extends java.lang.Object
    KotlinFlags represent a collection of flags in the metadata. When implementing this interface, it is only expected that you override getOwnProperties(). If you have any children you also need to implement getChildren()
